---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="苏打AB面 - SodaPlay">
  <div class="page">
    <a class="back" href="/">← 返回</a>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="icon">🆚</div>
      <h1 class="title">苏打AB面</h1>
      <p class="desc">每一题，都是一场苏打 1v1。<br/>两首歌摆在面前，你选哪一首？</p>
      <ul class="rules">
        <li>每道题给出两首苏打绿的歌，它们有某种相似或关联</li>
        <li>选择你更喜欢的那首，投出你的一票</li>
        <li>投票后可以看到所有玩家的选择比例</li>
        <li>每题可以改选，你的票会实时更新——来看看打粉们的默契度吧～</li>
      </ul>
      <a class="start-btn" href="/games/soda-ab-side/play">开始选择</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page {
    min-height: 100vh;
    min-height: 100dvh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 24px 16px;
    background: linear-gradient(160deg, #9B7FD4 0%, #B89AE8 30%, #D4C1F0 60%, #F0EAF8 100%);
  }

  .back {
    position: absolute;
    top: 20px;
    left: 20px;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .back:hover {
    color: #FFFFFF;
  }

  .card {
    text-align: center;
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border-radius: 24px;
    padding: 48px 32px;
    max-width: 400px;
    width: 100%;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .icon {
    font-size: 4rem;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .title {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--color-text);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  .desc {
    margin-top: 16px;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .rules {
    margin-top: 20px;
    padding: 0;
    list-style: none;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .rules li {
    position: relative;
    padding: 8px 0 8px 20px;
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .rules li::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 15px;
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #9B7FD4;
  }

  .rules strong {
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .start-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 28px;
    padding: 14px 48px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #9B7FD4, #B89AE8);
    color: #FFFFFF;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    border-radius: 50px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(155, 127, 212, 0.3);
  }

  .start-btn:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 24px rgba(155, 127, 212, 0.4);
  }

  .start-btn:active {
    transform: scale(0.97);
  }

  @media (min-width: 640px) {
    .card {
      padding: 56px 40px;
    }

    .title {
      font-size: 2.4rem;
    }
  }
</style>
